paper_title: Integer group determinants for ${\rm C}_{4} \rtimes {\rm C}_{4}$
abstract: Let ${\rm C}_{4}$ be the cyclic group of order $4$. We determine all possible values of the integer group determinant of ${\rm C}_{4} \rtimes {\rm C}_{4}$.
publication_venue: arXiv admin note: text overlap with arXiv:2303.08489
